        pygame.init()
        pygame.display.set_caption(TITLE)
        pygame.display.set_icon(ICON)
        self.screen = pygame.display.set_mode((SCREEN_WIDTH, SCREEN_HEIGHT))
        self.clock = pygame.time.Clock()
        self.playing = False
        self.game_speed = 10
        self.x_pos_bg = 0
